设置工作路径以及加载所需要的R包

setwd("G:/图片复现/1.barplot_通路富集/")
suppressMessages(library("ggplot2"))
suppressMessages(library("dplyr"))
suppressMessages(library("RColorBrewer"))

读取数据，并对数据进行筛选和排序

#读取富集结果
term_data = read.delim("1.group_A-vs-B-Up.Reactome.xls",sep="\t")
#过滤掉小于2个基因的term
term_data = term_data[which(term_data["Count"]>2), ]
#对数据按照Q值的log10排序
term_data = term_data %>% arrange(-log10(qvalue)) 
#把term设置为因子格式，固定顺序
term_data$Description = factor(term_data$Description, levels = unique(term_data$Description))

根据数据绘制初步图形

p = ggplot(term_data,aes(x = -log10(qvalue), y = Description )) + 
           geom_bar(stat="identity", position=position_dodge())
  
p

为条形图添加颜色

p = ggplot(term_data,aes(x = -log10(qvalue), y = Description )) + 
    geom_bar(stat="identity", position=position_dodge(),aes(fill = -log10(qvalue)))
#设置颜色
myPalette <- colorRampPalette(rev(brewer.pal(n = 7,name = "RdYlBu")))
sc <- scale_fill_gradientn(colours = myPalette(100))

p = p + sc 

p

修改term字体颜色和大小

p = ggplot(term_data,aes(x = -log10(qvalue), y = Description )) + 
    geom_bar(stat="identity", position=position_dodge(),aes(fill = -log10(qvalue)))
myPalette <- colorRampPalette(rev(brewer.pal(n = 7,name = "RdYlBu")))
sc <- scale_fill_gradientn(colours = myPalette(100))
#根据基因数量为y轴字体设置颜色
col_y = as.character(term_data$Count)
p = p + sc + theme(axis.text.y=element_text(color = col_y, size = 8 ))

p

为图形添加边框，设置图例在绘图区域内，设置其大小和背景色

p = ggplot(term_data,aes(x = -log10(qvalue), y = Description )) + 
    geom_bar(stat="identity", position=position_dodge(), 
             color="black",linewidth = 0.7,width = 0.7, 
             aes(fill = -log10(qvalue)))

myPalette <- colorRampPalette(rev(brewer.pal(n = 7,name = "RdYlBu")))
sc <- scale_fill_gradientn(colours = myPalette(100))

col_y = as.character(term_data$Count)
p = p + sc + theme(axis.text.y=element_text(color = col_y, size = 8 ))
# 在theme中调整图例参数
p = p + theme(legend.position=c(1,0.1),legend.justification=c(1,0.1),
              legend.background = element_rect(fill = 'transparent'),
              legend.key.size=unit(4,'mm'), 
              legend.title = element_text(size = 10, hjust = 0.5), 
              legend.text = element_text(size = 8))
p

设置绘图区背景网格形式

p = ggplot(term_data,aes(x = -log10(qvalue), y = Description )) + 
    geom_bar(stat="identity", position=position_dodge(), 
             color="black",linewidth = 0.7,width = 0.7, 
             aes(fill = -log10(qvalue)))
myPalette <- colorRampPalette(rev(brewer.pal(n = 7,name = "RdYlBu")))
sc <- scale_fill_gradientn(colours = myPalette(100))

col_y = as.character(term_data$Count)
p = p + sc + theme(axis.text.y=element_text(color = col_y, size = 8 ))
p = p + theme(legend.position=c(1,0.1),legend.justification=c(1,0.1),
              legend.background = element_rect(fill = 'transparent'),
              legend.key.size=unit(4,'mm'), 
              legend.title = element_text(size = 10, hjust = 0.5), 
              legend.text = element_text(size = 8))
#设置背景网格形式，dashed虚线
p = p + theme(panel.grid.major.x = element_blank(), panel.grid.minor = element_blank(), 
              panel.grid.major.y = element_line(linetype = "dashed", color = "gray50"))
p

修改x轴和y轴标题，修改图例标题

p = ggplot(term_data,aes(x = -log10(qvalue), y = Description )) + 
    geom_bar(stat="identity", position=position_dodge(), 
             color="black",linewidth = 0.7,width = 0.7, 
             aes(fill = -log10(qvalue)))
myPalette <- colorRampPalette(rev(brewer.pal(n = 7,name = "RdYlBu")))
sc <- scale_fill_gradientn(colours = myPalette(100))

col_y = as.character(term_data$Count)
p = p + sc + theme(axis.text.y=element_text(color = col_y, size = 8 ))
p = p + theme(legend.position=c(1,0.1),legend.justification=c(1,0.1),
              legend.background = element_rect(fill = 'transparent'),
              legend.key.size=unit(4,'mm'), 
              legend.title = element_text(size = 10, hjust = 0.5), 
              legend.text = element_text(size = 8))
p = p + theme(panel.grid.major.x = element_blank(), panel.grid.minor = element_blank(), 
              panel.grid.major.y = element_line(linetype = "dashed", color = "gray50"))
# 修改图例和xy轴名称
p = p + labs(fill = expression(-log[10](qval))) + xlab(expression(-log[10](qval))) + ylab("")

p

为图片添加Reactome文字注释

p = ggplot(term_data,aes(x = -log10(qvalue), y = Description )) + 
    geom_bar(stat="identity", position=position_dodge(), 
             color="black",linewidth = 0.7,width = 0.7, 
             aes(fill = -log10(qvalue)))
myPalette <- colorRampPalette(rev(brewer.pal(n = 7,name = "RdYlBu")))
sc <- scale_fill_gradientn(colours = myPalette(100))

col_y = as.character(term_data$Count)
p = p + sc + theme(axis.text.y=element_text(color = col_y, size = 8 ))
p = p + theme(legend.position=c(1,0.1),legend.justification=c(1,0.1),
              legend.background = element_rect(fill = 'transparent'),
              legend.key.size=unit(4,'mm'), 
              legend.title = element_text(size = 10, hjust = 0.5), 
              legend.text = element_text(size = 8))
p = p + theme(panel.grid.major.x = element_blank(), panel.grid.minor = element_blank(), 
              panel.grid.major.y = element_line(linetype = "dashed", color = "gray50"))
p = p + labs(fill = expression(-log[10](qval))) + xlab(expression(-log[10](qval))) + ylab("")
#添加一个注释文字，并确定文字坐标位置
p = p + annotate("text", x = 45, y = 1.5, label = "Reactome", size = 5, fontface="bold")

p

保存图片

ggsave("barplot1.png", plot = p, width = 9, height = 6)
ggsave("barplot1.pdf", plot = p, width = 9, height = 6)
